<head>
  <style>
    button{ color: #fff; background: #2196f3; border: 1px solid #2196f3;
    padding: .5rem 1rem; font-size: 0.75rem; transition: background-color
    .2s,color .2s,border-color .2s,box-shadow .2s; border-radius: 3px;margin: 0
    auto; display:block; cursor: pointer;; text-align: center; box-shadow: 0 3px
    1px -2px #0003,0 2px 2px 0 #00000024,0 1px 5px 0 #0000001f;}
  </style>
</head>
<div
  style='background:rgb(255, 255, 255); color:#333; padding:1rem; border-radius:5px; width: 100%'
>
  <div style='width:100%; max-width:550px; display: block; margin: 0 auto'>
    <b>Hi
      <span style='color:#0d89ec'>{{username}}</span>,</b>
    <img
      src='{{img}}'
      alt='welcome image'
      style='width: 50%;max-width:250px; display:block; margin: 0.5rem auto; position:relative; top: 1rem'
    />
    Welcome to
    <span style='color:#0d89ec'>Krakky</span>!
    <br />
    <br />
    We are so glad you have chosen us to help you keep track of your
    project/buisness.
    <br />
    At Krakky we only stand for one thing and that is to make your life easier
    and not only yours but for everyone in your company.
    <br />
    The only thing you have to do now is confirming your email address by
    clicking the verify account button.
    <br />
    <br />
    <a href='{{urlVerify}}'><button>Verify account</button></a>
    <br />
    <br />
    If you didn't join Krakky click remove account button.
    <br />
    <br />
    <a href='{{urlDelete}}'><button>Remove account</button></a>
    <br />
    <br />
    Excited to have you aboard! Thanks!
    <br />
    <br />
    <span style='color:#0d89ec'>Krakky</span>
    Team
  </div>
</div>